  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Schwarz Group (the Group or the company) is one of the largest European discount retailers. It operates two types of discount food stores in Europe:   -  Lidl, limited range deep discount stores; and  -  Kaufland compact discount hypermarkets.   The purpose of the project is for the company to plan a large expansion program, involving the establishment of a number of new stores and hypermarkets in Central and Eastern Europe to be implemented over the next couple of years.</narrative>
  </description>
